DESCRIPTION-

This is a demo only but its a chance to try it before it gets released!

A hyper violent multiplayer gladiator combat game. WHAT GOES AROUND COMES AROUND!

History

A game born from getting back to basics.

Features

Fast and furious javelin throwing and gladius thrusting.
One hit kills that are as stylish as they are bloody.
Shifting arenas whose layouts change every round.
Mystery chests containing randomized weapons.
Trash-talking, back-slapping, multiplayer for up to 4 players.
